item.title: CVE-2020-1920|2024-08-04T06:54:00.363Z -- facebook -- react-native
item.description: A regular expression denial of service (ReDoS) vulnerability in the validateBaseUrl function can cause the application to use excessive resources, become unresponsive, or crash. This was introduced in react-native version 0.59.0 and fixed in version 0.64.1.
